data.description: Nestled in a serene neighborhood with a one-way in and out, this impeccable 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home embodies pristine living. Its spacious interior boasts cleanliness and charm, offering ample space for a growing family. Surrounded by top-rated schools, it ensures an enriching educational environment for children. With meticulous upkeep evident throughout, this residence promises a haven of comfort and tranquility. Experience the epitome of suburban living in this immaculate abode, where quality meets convenience in every corner.
